### {110}{}{History tends to repeat itself, like a time loop on a large scale. Written records date back more than five thousand and two hundred years ago... plenty of data to be analyzed. Let me give you an example from recent history [he smiles.] The first Great War in the beginning of the 20th century taught people how to implement ancient war tactics into modern warfare, forcing them to build more sophisticated and devastating weapons. Every following war brought more casualties and destruction...}
{110}{}{历史往往会重演，就像一个大规模的时间循环。书面记录可以追溯到五千二百年前。。。大量数据有待分析。让我给你举一个近代史上的例子[他笑着说]20世纪初的第一次大战教会了人们如何将古代战争战术运用到现代战争中，迫使他们制造更先进、更具破坏性的武器。接下来的每一场战争都带来了更多的伤亡和破坏。。。 -- History tends to repeat itself, like a time loop on a large scale. Written records date back more than five thousand and two hundred years ago... plenty of data to be analyzed. Let me give you an example from recent history [he smiles.] The first Great War in the beginning of the 20th century taught people how to implement ancient war tactics into modern warfare, forcing them to build more sophisticated and devastating weapons. Every following war brought more casualties and destruction...}
### {111}{}{True, go on...}
