### {112}{}{...Having a bigger weapon than your enemies was their motto. Waging their wars over the centuries left our world in a terrible state. Pollution caused all kinds of sudden weather changes, irradiated the wasteland. One of our projects is to built an environmental armor as we call it. It will use multi functional materials designed to withstand both weather effects and high energy particles penetration.}
{112}{}{…拥有比敌人更大的武器是他们的座右铭。几个世纪以来，他们发动的战争使我们的世界处于一种可怕的状态。污染导致各种天气突变，照射到荒地上。我们的项目之一是建造一种我们称之为“环保装甲”的装甲。它将使用多功能材料，设计用于抵御天气影响和高能粒子穿透。 -- ...Having a bigger weapon than your enemies was their motto. Waging their wars over the centuries left our world in a terrible state. Pollution caused all kinds of sudden weather changes, irradiated the wasteland. One of our projects is to built an environmental armor as we call it. It will use multi functional materials designed to withstand both weather effects and high energy particles penetration.}
