{133}{}{把它看作是一种必要或预防措施。至于未来。。。如果明天只会有更多的冲突和破坏，那就没有了。如果我们继续走这条自我毁灭的道路，我们自己的生存可能会受到威胁。因此，我们在这里试图让人们重新开始思考，为了我们大家。 -- Think of it as a necessity or precautionary measure. As for the future... there's none if tomorrow only holds more conflicts and destruction. Our own existence might be in jeopardy if we continue this road towards self destruction. So we're trying here to make people start thinking again, for the better of us all.}
